                </div>
                <a href="https://www.example.com/book-now" class="cta-button">Book Now</a>
            </div>
            <div class="call-to-action">
                <p>Act fast and take advantage of this limited-time offer. Don't miss out on transforming your outdoor space into a lush, green oasis.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>If you no longer wish to receive our emails, please <a href="mailto:unsubscribe@example.com" class="unsubscribe">unsubscribe here</a>.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
